  "prompt": "Which is best IT institute in Delhi?",
  "response": "Determining the \"best\" IT institute in Delhi can be subjective and depends on specific criteria such as the courses offered, faculty qualifications, placement records, infrastructure, and student reviews. However, some well-regarded IT institutes in Delhi include:\n\n1. **NIIT** - A well-known name in IT education offering a range of courses and certification programs.\n\n2. **Aptech** - Offers comprehensive courses in IT with a focus on practical and industry-relevant skills.\n\n3. **Coding Ninjas** - Known for its coding courses and bootcamps that help students master programming.\n\n4. **JetKing** - Specializes in hardware and networking training.\n\n5. **IIHT (Indian Institute of Hardware Technology)** - Offers professional courses in hardware and networking.\n\n6. **Ducat** - Provides training in various IT fields, including software development and network administration.\n\n7. **Simplilearn** - Offers online certification courses across various tech domains with a focus on advanced technologies.\n\n8. **IIIT Delhi (Indraprastha Institute of Information Technology)** - Known for its rigorous academic programs and research opportunities.\n\nBefore deciding, it\u2019s important to research each institute based on your career goals, visit campuses if possible, attend demo classes, and speak to alumni or current students to get a better understanding of the institute\u2019s offerings.",
